			<div class="dablink">This article is about the punctuation mark.  For the Asian-American magazine, see <a href="/wiki/Hyphen_(magazine)" title="Hyphen (magazine)">Hyphen (magazine)</a>.  For the science fiction fanzine, see <a href="/wiki/Hyphen_(fanzine)" title="Hyphen (fanzine)">Hyphen (fanzine)</a>.  For the architectural element, see <a href="/wiki/Hyphen_(architecture)" title="Hyphen (architecture)">Hyphen (architecture)</a>.</div>
